&lt;p&gt;The USB disks can be identified by the Partition UUID, UUID of the disk, by path, by label of the disk and also by disk sequence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;By UUID(Universally Unique Identifier)&lt;span class=&#34;absolute -mt-20&#34; id=&#34;by-uuiduniversally-unique-identifier&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#by-uuiduniversally-unique-identifier&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;code-block relative mt-6 first:mt-0 group/code&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;filename&#34;&gt;by uuid&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;code-block-3&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;$ cat /etc/fstab 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;UUID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;3341b336-0c26-4079-b3aa-faca8e2dd8b6 /               ext4    &lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;errors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;remount-ro &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;UUID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;53b53d97-b5e4-43fe-b560-2a01f119b6cf none            swap    sw              &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;/dev/sr0        /media/cdrom0   udf,iso9660 user,noauto     &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;$ ls -ltrh /dev/disk/by-uuid/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;total &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;lrwxrwxrwx &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; root root &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt; Aug &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;22&lt;/span&gt; 10:40 3341b336-0c26-4079-b3aa-faca8e2dd8b6 -&amp;gt; ../../sda1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;lrwxrwxrwx &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; root root &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt; Aug &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;22&lt;/span&gt; 10:40 53b53d97-b5e4-43fe-b560-2a01f119b6cf -&amp;gt; ../../sda5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;lrwxrwxrwx &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; root root  &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt; Aug &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;29&lt;/span&gt; 09:49 2010-10-06-11-43-04-00 -&amp;gt; ../../sdb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;opacity-0 transition group-hover/code:opacity-100 flex gap-1 absolute m-[11px] right-0 top-8&#34;&gt;
